{
  "stem": "5430.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I guess we were just selling off the items that my father bought before the war.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Was it legal?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't think there was any questions.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There wasn't that much of authority really.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The military was pretty much governing-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] quite frankly, I don't remember what-- what kind of a political situation was there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And at that point-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] oh, before-- let me backtrack a little bit to give us a little relationship between my brothers and-- and I.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My oldest brother, George was in the Polish army and was called up before the war.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, he was-- he was born in 1913.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he was 26.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he was in the Polish army.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he-- I know he was in the anti-aircraft lights-- what do you call it-- the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my other brother, Jacob, was of military age already.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But they didn't-- I don't think they had enough uniforms for them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were ordered to just to get out of Warsaw and more or less follow the army wherever they went.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- the Polish army kept retreating towards the Russian border.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they-- they were either go to Romania or something like that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They-- they kept retreating.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And at that time, the Russians decided to come in and occupy the eastern part of Poland.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And by that time, they overtook the-- the Polish army.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I know my brother said he decided at that time to just take off the uniforms.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They disbanded.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There was really chaos there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he became a civilian under the Russian occupation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But my other brother, Jacob-- Yakob, we used to call him-- who was told to follow the army, also wound up under the Russian occupation, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
